    "path": "learningPathways[0].pathways[0].studyTitles[2].titleLevel3",
    "text": "Truth Unlocked (1)"
  },
  {
    "path": "learningPathways[0].pathways[0].studyTitles[2].description",
    "text": "<b>Truth Unlocked, Volume 1: Christian Belief</b><br><br>Eight studies to help you understand the essential truths revealed by God in the Bible. We cannot live godly lives unless we understand Biblical truth and apply it as the foundation for our lives. <i>Truth Unlocked</i> is also a helpful refresher for those who have been Christians for some time and wish to review the basics of their faith. You may be surprised by what you learn!"
  },
  {
