  {
    "path": "learningPathways[0].pathways[1].studyTitles[2].description",
    "text": "<b>Truth Unlocked, Volume 2: Christian Living</b><br><br>Eight studies to help you understand the essential truths revealed by God in the Bible. We cannot live godly lives unless we understand Biblical truth and apply it as the foundation for our lives. <i>Truth Unlocked</i> is also a helpful refresher for those who have been Christians for some time and wish to review the basics of their faith. You may be surprised by what you learn!"
  },
  {
    "path": "learningPathways[0].pathways[1].studyTitles[3].titleLevel3",
    "text": "Grow in Christ (1)"
  },
  {
    "path": "learningPathways[0].pathways[1].studyTitles[3].description",
    "text": "<b>Grow in Christ (Discipleship course)</b><br><br>Are you growing in Christ? God wants all his children to grow in Jesus. If you are not growing, this studies will help you work out what is wrong and how to put it right. If you are growing, they will help you grow more. Working through Scripture, each session combines close reading with personal reflection. (We have split this course into several volumes. Do volume 1 first \u2013 but if you've already done that, carry on with the next volume.)"
  },
  {
